subs.text: I asked DALL-E for help in creating an icon for Feed Hunter. I can't imagine an art director at an agency not using AI to play around with ideas for logos, symbols, ads, whatever. What I arrived at was a tennis racket trying to hit a cheeseburger.
A quick collaboration for an icon for Feed Hunter.
PS: I didn't use it, instead I went with Wikipedia's illustration of a hunter.
